{"type":null,"faqId":16804,"title":"荣耀畅玩4X NFC无法读取银行卡？","answer":"<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">您好，请按以下步骤确认：</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">1）首先确认机器型号是CherryCL10；</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">2）确定NFC图标是否在右上角状态栏出现。</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">3）确认手机后盖是否盖严实，由于CherryCL10后盖模具设计在天线部位有个卡口，如果后盖没有盖好，会造成天线接触不良无法读卡；</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">4）确认手机后壳背部是否有NFC天线，且天线金属触点良好，且NFC天线的金属触点是否有触痕。用手触摸天线的金属触点是否突出，以保证天线可以接触正常。</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">5）确定读卡时，卡片位于手机背部NFC标识区域</p>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\">6）确定读卡时，手机处于亮屏解锁状态。</p>\n<br>\n<p align=\"\" style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;\"></p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":1,"unUseful":7,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9433","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1417249447000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,Cherry-CL20","visitedTimes":1867,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"荣耀畅玩4X,Che1-CL10,4x,NFC,银行卡","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}